messages.message: Hey team, table extraction isn't extracting all rows on this document ("extract all tables" with advanced table & checkbox extraction turned on). Missing ~30% of the rows on this 4 page doc
Skips almost the entire 3rd page. Catches the first 3 rows of the last table on the third page, and then misses the last 3 rows of the last table (on the 4th page)

Lesser problem - it's not properly identifying breaks in the tables. Example shown here: it's extracting Claim ID 2620 and Claim ID 2802 as the same table. Happens multiple times (AI Hub only extracts 3 total tables when there are 11).
